---
title: Apricot-Glazed Turkey Roast with Roasted Potatoes and Nectarine Chutney
description: Tonight's star-studded feast comes complete with an apricot-glazed roast turkey, crispy roasted potatoes, juicy nectarine chutney and crispy sugar snap peas!
